divs: Sighting DetailsDidn't see anything. Noise and house shook. Looked outside. Didn't see anything. Automatic lights were on by garage. Went back to bed. Today July 22, 2011. Walked back home across the commons and saw a visible circle in the grass outside my living room window. Wow! Pretty strange. No idea what it is or what caused it.
Summary: Heard loud noise, got up looked out of window garage lights were on.
